Package: reformatFilePath
Title: RStudio Add-In Formatting File Path
Version: 0.0.0.1
Authors@R: "Konrad Zdeb <konrad.zdeb@me.com> [aut,cre]"
Description: This simple package formats file path string using 'file.path'
  call. The add-in can optionally write the 'file.path' in 'normalizePath'
  call and change default 'fsep' argument.
Depends: R (>= 3.3.0)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
Imports:
    shiny (>= 0.13),
    formatR,
    miniUI (>= 0.1.1),
    rstudioapi (>= 0.5),
Suggests: 
    testthat,
    checkmate,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    here
VignetteBuilder: knitr
